'''2021年巴塔爆炸事故'''是在2021年3月7日發生於[[赤道幾内亞|赤道幾内亞]]最大城及前首都[[巴塔_(赤道几内亚)|巴塔]]一處軍營的四次連環爆炸事件<ref name="SwissInfo">{{cite news |title=Una cadena de explosiones causa 17 muertos y 420 heridos en Guinea Ecuatorial |url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/spa/guinea-ecuatorial-explosiones--previsión-_una-cadena-de-explosiones-causa-17-muertos-y-420-heridos-en-guinea-ecuatorial/46428580 |access-date=2021-03-08 |agency=SwissInfo |date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311050411/https://www.swissinfo.ch/spa/guinea-ecuatorial-explosiones--previsi%C3%B3n-_una-cadena-de-explosiones-causa-17-muertos-y-420-heridos-en-guinea-ecuatorial/46428580 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，前三次爆炸在[[西非時間|當地時間]]（[[UTC+1|UTC+1]]）下午三時左右接連發生，兩個小時後再發生另一次爆炸<ref name="SwissInfo" />。

爆炸造成至少105人死亡<ref>{{cite news|title=Bata blast: Satellite images show Equatorial Guinea destruction|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-56337856|date=2021-03-10|work=BBC News|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2021-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311114415/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-56337856|dead-url=no}}</ref>，超過615人受傷<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.al.com/news/2021/03/at-least-15-dead-400-wounded-in-explosions-in-equatorial-guinea.html|title=At least 20 dead, 600 wounded in explosions in Equatorial Guinea|first=The Associated|last=Press|date=2021-03-07|website=al|access-date=2021-03-08|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506054643/https://www.al.com/news/2021/03/at-least-15-dead-400-wounded-in-explosions-in-equatorial-guinea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦對軍營附近地區造成嚴重破壞<ref>{{Cite web|title=Huge explosions rock Equatorial Guinea's main city|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-56311677|access-date=2021-03-07|website=BBC|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506054648/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-56311677|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/equatorial-guinea-bata-explosions/2021/03/07/cf9b27f4-7f66-11eb-9ca6-54e187ee4939_story.html|title=Massive explosions rock Equatorial Guinea’s largest city; at least 17 dead, hundreds injured|first=Max|last=Bearak|via=www.washingtonpost.com|access-date=2021-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308000620/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/equatorial-guinea-bata-explosions/2021/03/07/cf9b27f4-7f66-11eb-9ca6-54e187ee4939_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Staff|first=Reuters|date=2021-03-07|title=Explosions kill at least 20 in Equatorial Guinea city of Bata - local TV station|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-equatorial-blast-idUSKBN2AZ0IA|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506060227/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-equatorial-blast-idUSKBN2AZ0IA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[赤道幾内亞總統|赤道幾内亞總統]][[特奧多羅·奧比昂·恩圭馬·姆巴索戈|特奧多羅·奧比昂·恩圭馬·姆巴索戈]]事後發表全國電視講話，將事故肇因歸咎於儲藏軍火方法不當<ref>{{cite news|first1=Max|last1=Bearak|accessdate=2021-03-07|title=Massive explosions rock Equatorial Guinea’s largest city; 17 dead, hundreds injured|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/equatorial-guinea-bata-explosions/2021/03/07/cf9b27f4-7f66-11eb-9ca6-54e187ee4939_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|issn=0190-8286|via=www.washingtonpost.com|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308000620/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/equatorial-guinea-bata-explosions/2021/03/07/cf9b27f4-7f66-11eb-9ca6-54e187ee4939_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且稱幾乎全市建築物均受損<ref name="SwissInfo" />。他也呼籲國際社會伸出援手<ref name="SwissInfo" />。爆炸發生之後，該國副總統{{le|特奧多羅·恩圭馬·奧比昂·曼格|Teodoro Nguema Obiang Mangue}}趕赴現場視察<ref name="SwissInfo" />。赤道幾內亞外长会见多国大使请求援助<ref>{{cite news |title=赤道几内亚外长请求国际援助：我们不仅面临疫情 还发生大爆炸悲剧 |url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2021-03-08/1648364.html |accessdate=2021-03-08 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506054737/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2021-03-08/1648364.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

